OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FMan without hands or legs  
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fis left without carers     
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, A man born without hands or legs has   
OL,6, been told he will soon no longer get a 
OL,7, daily visit from a care worker to help 
OL,8, him shower and get dressed.            
OL,10,FDJ Calvert told BBC News NI: "I've been
OL,11,Flet down - and I'm not the only one."  
OL,13,FIt was proof that Northern Ireland's   
OL,14,Fhealth and social care system had      
OL,15,F"crashed", said the 49-year-old.       
OL,17,FHis care is provided by an independent 
OL,18,Ffirm on behalf of the Northern Health  
OL,19,FTrust. The trust said it was "urgently 
OL,20,Fseeking an alternative care provider". 
